  "displayName": "Rustem Feyzkhanov",
  "headline": "",
  "summary": "Rustem Feyzkhanov is the Engineering Manager for the Snorkel AI Platform team, building data-centric AI solutions. His background includes roles as ML Engineering Manager at Instrumental (manufacturing AI) and an engineer at Astro Digital (satellite imagery AI). A prominent voice on leveraging cloud infrastructure for AI, Rustem is the author of the book “Serverless Deep Learning with TensorFlow and AWS Lambda.” He is a seasoned speaker who has shared his expertise at numerous prestigious conferences, including O'Reilly Strata, O'Reilly Software Architecture, and AI DevWorld. His presentations focus on the practical application of cloud-native AWS services for building efficient and scalable deep learning training and inference pipelines. In addition to his professional and speaking engagements, Rustem is the creator of several popular open-source repositories on GitHub that provide valuable resources for the community. His current interests lie in pushing the boundaries of serverless for AI/ML, tackling the unique challenges of hosting large language models (LLMs), and engineering robust, production-grade ML workflows using AWS infrastructure.",
